entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You recovered the ID cards stolen by Shinn's muggers near Mos Eisley.
entries.journal_entry_description: A local band of muggers led by Vaigon Shinn has been stealing ID cards from people. Recover those stolen cards from Shinn's muggers.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Recover the stolen ID cards from Vaigon Shinn's muggers. Use whatever force is necessary.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Peawp R'dawc and let her know you recovered some of the stolen ID cards.
